column2: SELECT     m.ra AS ra_spec, m.dec AS dec_spec, m.z, m.plate, m.mjd, m.fiberid    n.objid, n.distance,     o.ra AS ra_photo, o.dec AS dec_photo, o.petror5#_u as r5#_u, o.petror5#_g as r5#_g, o.petror5#_r as r5#_r, o.petror5#_i as r5#_i, o.petror5#_z as r5#_z, o.petror9#_u as r9#_u, o.petror9#_g as r9#_g, o.petror9#_r as r9#_r, o.petror9#_i as r9#_i, o.petror9#_z as r9#_z into mydb.sdss_r from MyDB.sdss_r1 AS m     OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     LEFT JOIN photoobjall AS o ON n.objid=o.objid
